name: Crypto Sharks#2
description: Join the crypto-shark revolution! Join us on a journey to save our oceans and help build the biggest community-owned crypto mining farm in the world! Crypto Sharks is a collection of 11,416 unique ocean predators that live and swim on the Ethereum blockchain. Step into our fin-tastic world and help protect our seas by adopting these majestic animals as your own. Yup you heard it, 1 Minted Crypto Shark = 1 Adopted shark. Get ready because we are just getting started!
